NK010(tha)038:1: ru dra'i keng rus las grub pa'i ri rab chen
NK010(tha)038:2: po mtshon cha sna tshogs 'bar ba'i nags tshal 'khrigs
NK010(tha)038:3: pa dug rlangs dang me ri dmar nag tu 'bar
NK010(tha)038:4: ba / mthong ba tsam gyi 'jigs shing ya nga ba'i rang bzhin can /
NK010(tha)038:5: khrag gi rgya mtsho chen po rba klong drag tu
NK010(tha)038:6: 'khrugs pa'i dbus nas thol gyis skyes pa de la
NK010(tha)038:7: ye shes 'jig rten pa'i dregs byed thams cad kyi
NK010(tha)038:9: 'jig rten khams kyi nad mtshon dug sogs drag po'i
NK010(tha)038:10: rdzas kyi nus pa thams cad bsdus nas thim par
NK010(tha)038:11: gyur / rdo yi zor de las drag po mtshon
NK010(tha)038:12: cha'i char bab pas dgra bgegs byad ma thams cad
NK010(tha)038:13: bsgral ba'i sha yi ri bo khrag gi rgya mtsho
NK010(tha)038:14: rus pa'i gram khrod chen po stong gsum dang mnyam
NK010(tha)038:15: gyur / pa la / khro bo khro mo ma
NK010(tha)038:16: mo mkha' 'gro phra men las byed lha srin sde
NK010(tha)038:17: brgyad thams cad gad brgyangs di ri ri rol zhing
NK010(tha)038:18: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi bgo ba'i bka' la nyan
NK010(tha)038:19: nas dgra bgegs bzlog bsad kyi las la rngams par
NK010(tha)038:20: gyur / pa la / gyur / khrag skyems mchod la /
NK010(tha)038:22: brgyud pa dgu ldan rig 'dzin bla ma'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)038:23: dus 'dir bstan pa gnyan la dgra dar zhing //
NK010(tha)038:24: bstan 'dzin rnal 'byor rnams la dgra langs na //
NK010(tha)038:25: ma g.yel thugs rje khros pa'i brtul zhugs kyis //
NK010(tha)038:26: drang srong dmod pa las kyi skur bzhengs nas //
NK010(tha)038:27: dgra bgegs sha khrag mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)038:28: rigs sngags rbod gtong byed pa'i dam nyams 'di'i //
NK010(tha)038:29: srung ba'i gur khang rdo rje'i mtshon gyis choms //
NK010(tha)038:30: 'go ba'i lha srung gnod pa'i bdud du phobs //
NK010(tha)038:31: dmod pa'i sngags nus kho la smin par gyis //
NK010(tha)038:32: lus la mtshon cha sna tshogs char phobs la //
NK010(tha)038:33: rnam shes lus srog rten dang phrol la thongs //
NK010(tha)038:34: gnod byed byad ma bsad pa'i dus //
NK010(tha)038:35: rbod gtong rig sngags bzlog pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)038:36: mi mthun 'gal rkyen bzlog pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)038:37: ye shes klong dgu 'bar ba'i gzhal yas nas //
NK010(tha)038:38: rab 'byams yi dam khro bo'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK010(tha)038:39: dgra bgegs sha khrag sogs gong ltar /
NK010(tha)038:40: khyad par phrin las drag po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK010(tha)038:41: lha mchog rdo rje gzhon nu yab dang yum //
NK010(tha)038:42: sras mchog khro bcu yab yum phra men dang //
NK010(tha)038:43: sgo skyong phur srung dam can dregs pa'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)038:45: khams gsum sa dgu gnas kyi dur khrod nas //
NK010(tha)038:46: ye shes 'jig rten las kyi d+aa ki ma //
NK010(tha)038:47: 'bum phrag yangs pa chen po'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK010(tha)038:49: phrin las drag po sgrol byed gzhal yas nas //
NK010(tha)038:50: ye shes 'jig rten bstan srung dregs byed tshogs //
NK010(tha)038:51: snang srid lha srin sde brgyad 'khor dang bcas //
NK010(tha)038:54: dgongs su gsol lo rab 'byams rtsa ba gsum //
NK010(tha)038:55: nyes med bdag la 'tshe zhing bar gcod pa'i //
NK010(tha)038:56: dgra bgegs byad ma bsgral ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)038:57: thugs dam ma g.yel bcol pa'i las 'di sgrubs //
NK010(tha)038:58: mkha' mnyam chos dbyings drag po'i gzhal yas nas //
NK010(tha)038:59: rab khros rtsa gsum dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)038:60: 'bar ba'i sku mchog sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK010(tha)038:61: phyag na sgrol byed drag po'i mtshon cha bsnams //
NK010(tha)038:62: zhal nas drag sngags dmod pa'i thog ser 'phro //
NK010(tha)038:63: ye shes thugs rje khros pa'i brtul zhugs kyis //
NK010(tha)038:64: mi mthun bar chad bzlog pa'i las la bzhengs //
NK010(tha)038:65: dgra bgegs byad ma bsad pa'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)038:66: rbod gtong rigs sngags bzlog pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)038:67: mi mthun 'gal rkyen bzlog pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)038:68: dgra bgegs byad ma lha dang bcas pa yi //
NK010(tha)038:69: srog chod dbugs phrog sha zo khrag 'thung la //
NK010(tha)038:70: rdul phran tsam yang med par brlag mdzad de //
NK010(tha)038:71: rig 'dzin bdag cag 'khor dang ltos par bcas //
NK010(tha)038:72: mi mthun phyogs las rnam par rgyal ba yi //
NK010(tha)038:73: 'jigs med rdo rje'i rgyal mtshan deng 'dir sgrengs //
NK010(tha)038:74: yid la re ba'i don kun 'grub pa dang //
NK010(tha)038:75: bcol ba'i phrin las ma lus 'grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)038:76: ces byas la bzlog sngags dmigs pa gsal bzhin bzla /
NK010(tha)038:78: gdug pa'i rdo zor chen po de nyid dgra bo
NK010(tha)038:79: byad ma gang du gnas pa'i steng nas thog brgyab
NK010(tha)038:81: lus srog yul khams dang bcas pa sgo nga brag la bcar ba ltar brlag nas /
NK010(tha)038:82: 'byung bzhi'i dkyil 'khor bzhi dang bsres te rnam shes
NK010(tha)038:83: nam mkha' drag po e dbyings mu med pa mtha'
NK010(tha)038:84: bral chos nyid kyi klong du thim nas /
NK010(tha)038:85: gnod pa'i bsam sbyor nam yang mi skye bar bsam la 'phang ngo //
NK010(tha)038:86: dgos pa'i dbang gis chu stag zla ba dgu pa'i
NK010(tha)038:87: nyer dgu la 'jam dpal dgyes ba'i rdo rjes yid
NK010(tha)038:88: las phral shar dge legs kyi rgyal mtshan bsgreng bar
